'''大学美式足球季后赛'''（{{lang-en|College Football Playoff}}，简称{{lang|en|CFP}}）是美国大学[[美式足球|美式足球]]的年度赛事，参赛学校来自[[国家大学体育协会|国家大学体育协会]]（{{lang|en|NCAA}}）[[NCAA第一级别|第一级别]][[NCAA第一级别美式足球碗赛分区|美式足球碗赛分区]]（{{lang|en|FBS}}）。该项赛事于2014赛季开始创立，其前身为{{link-en|冠军盃系列赛|Bowl Championship Series}}。<ref name=McMurphy>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/9204021/football-playoff-name-site|title=Football playoff has name and site|last=McMurphy|first=Brett|date=April 24, 2013|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=April 24, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215744/http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/9204021/football-playoff-name-site|dead-url=no}}</ref>每年共有四支队伍参赛，包含两场半决赛与一场全国冠军赛。<ref name="usat">{{cite news |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/ncaaf/2013/04/24/college-football-playoff-questions-and-answers/2111419/ |title=Questions and answers for the College Football Playoff |last=Wolken |first=Dan |date=April 25, 2013 |publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |accessdate=April 25, 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106233521/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/ncaaf/2013/04/24/college-football-playoff-questions-and-answers/2111419/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

每年的两场半决赛会[[玫瑰盃|玫瑰盃]]、[[砂糖盃|砂糖盃]]、[[橘子盃|橘子盃]]、[[棉花盃|棉花盃]]、[[喜庆盃|喜庆盃]]、[[桃子盃|桃子盃]]这六大盃赛（合称为“新年六盃”）中轮流选择，日期一般为每年的最后一个星期五、星期六或[[元旦|元旦]]。<ref name="espncom-cfpchanges">{{cite web|title=College Football Playoff tweaks dates in upcoming seasons|url=http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/17163763/college-football-playoff-moves-some-new-year-eve-dates|website=ESPN.com|accessdate=28 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801075419/http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/17163763/college-football-playoff-moves-some-new-year-eve-dates|dead-url=no}}</ref>全国冠军赛则在半决赛六天之后算起的第一个星期一举行。<ref name="espn-official">{{cite web|title=Playoff plan to run through 2025|author=Heather Dinch|publisher=ESPN.com|date=June 27, 2012|accessdate=August 10, 2013|url=http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/8099187/ncaa-presidents-approve-four-team-college-football-playoff-beginning-2014|archive-date=2012-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627034357/http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/8099187/ncaa-presidents-approve-four-team-college-football-playoff-beginning-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>

CFP并非NCAA官方举办的赛事，因而美式足球盃赛分区（{{lang|en|FBS}}）也是目前NCAA所有项目中唯一一个每年没有由NCAA主办的全国总决赛的项目。<ref>{{cite news|author1=C.N.|title=The business of college football: Undisputed champs in a disputed sport|url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/gametheory/2015/01/business-college-football|website=The Economist|accessdate=6 September 2015|date=14 January 2015|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824174448/https://www.economist.com/blogs/gametheory/2015/01/business-college-football|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=dodd>{{cite web|last1=Dodd|first1=Dennis|title=Fringe benefit of College Football Playoff? No more mythical titles|url=http://www.cbssports.com/collegefootball/writer/dennis-dodd/24596069/fringe-benefit-of-college-football-playoff-no-more-mythical-titles|website=CBS Sports|accessdate=6 September 2015|date=24 June 2014|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310075217/http://www.cbssports.com/collegefootball/writer/dennis-dodd/24596069/fringe-benefit-of-college-football-playoff-no-more-mythical-titles|dead-url=no}}</ref>

